Prerequisites
-------------

* CentOS Linux release = 7.6.1810
* gcc-c++ >= 4.8.5-36.el7_6.2
* boost169-devel >= 1.69.0-1.el7
* imake >= 1:3.82-23.el7

Install
-------

The basic procedure is:

  make
  make install

Variables controlling the build process:

* GCC_BASE [/usr]
* CXX [/usr/bin/g++]
* BOOST_ROOT [/usr]
* BOOST_INCLUDEDIR [/usr/include/boost169]
* BOOST_LIBRARYDIR [/usr/lib/boost169]
* CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH (or CPATH ) for gtest include directory
* LIBRARY_PATH for gtest libraries
